divs: sighting detailsme and my friend were camping and we were looking up at the stars and we saw a satelite and we thought that was pretty cool so we kept looking and we saw this white ball of light brighter than all the other stars and it was moving vary fast south\ south east it was dipping in and out so it obviously wasn't a plane and the height it was at it could'nt possibly be a helicopter and then it started to move up and south and it dissapeared for about 2 seconds and then shot back into our atmosphere and was gone i feel crazy but i know what i saw.
